{"title":"Save on these Microsoft 365 single-user and family plans, now starting at $45","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2225341/save-on-these-microsoft-365-single-user-and-family-plans-now-starting-at-45.html","date":1706868000000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/microsoft-365-family-12-month-subscription-up-to-6-people?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=microsoft-365-family-12-month-subscription-up-to-6-people&amp;utm_term=scsf-589877&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000000EvzJIAS&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2225341-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Secure your favorite Microsoft Office apps</a>, access them from different devices, and lock in heightened security with one tool: Microsoft 365. For a limited time, a personal plan (1 user) is only $44.99 (reg. $69), and a family plan (up to 6 users) is only $74.99 (reg. $99). </p>\n\n\n\n<p>To start, you’ll get access to Microsoft Office’s top-rated productivity apps, including Word, Excel, PowerPoint, OneNote, and Teams. You’ll also get Outlook, a helpful platform for families with hectic schedules and business owners who need to manage their communication via email.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Microsoft 365 also offers users cloud storage from OneDrive, with the personal plan providing 1TB and the family plan providing 6TB (1TB per user). Plus, users can enjoy peace of mind with their activities on Microsoft 365, as there’s <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/microsoft-365-personal-12-month-subscription?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=microsoft-365-personal-12-month-subscription&amp;utm_term=scsf-589876&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000000EvzJIAS&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2225341-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Microsoft Defender in the background, which monitors your device for malware and other digital threats</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, there’s Microsoft Editor for more confident writing, Clipchamp for easier video editing and creation, and new features and updates are always added to your Microsoft 365 subscription.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For a limited time, get a <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/microsoft-365-personal-12-month-subscription?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=microsoft-365-personal-12-month-subscription&amp;utm_term=scsf-589876&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000000EvzJIAS&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2225341-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">1-year subscription to the Microsoft 365 Personal Plan</a> (1 user) for just $44.99 or a <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/microsoft-365-family-12-month-subscription-up-to-6-people?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=microsoft-365-family-12-month-subscription-up-to-6-people&amp;utm_term=scsf-589877&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000000EvzJIAS&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2225341-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">1-year subscription to the Microsoft 365 Family Plan</a> (up to 6 users) for just $74.99.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/microsoft-365-personal-12-month-subscription?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral-cta&amp;utm_campaign=microsoft-365-personal-12-month-subscription&amp;utm_term=scsf-589876&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000000EvzJIAS&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2225341-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\"> </a></p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://cdnp3.stackassets.com/694a44d17c6b89237aa7bb10124438521d3393a9/store/bc24c4355b731cfcc0a2